"Looking at the sky together"
Looking at the sky with you, The only thing I want, the same sky that sent you to  your mommy and me, the sky that I thank every day, the same sky that I want to give you in this life, the same sky from where one day, I pray God, very far, I'm going to look at you protecting you with all my love.
From this sky you came, my luminous star that illuminated my path, my blessed Angel that showed me another side of life.
I want to stay like this, looking at the sky, the same sky where all dreams go.
Mine today is to make a dream of your whole life because you have already fulfilled mine by arriving in my arms and filling my soul with love every second.
I ask heaven to let me look at your eyes when they will laugh, wiped the tears away from them, I ask heaven to protect you and fill your life with the brightest rainbows.
Thank you my love for being the heaven I always dreamed of, thank you God for allowing me to live this dream.
I love you my princess and happy Father's Day to me.

Mirar el cielo contigo, nada más puedo querer, el mismo cielo que te envió a mí y a tu mami, el cielo que cada día agradezco, el mismo cielo que quiero regalarte en esta vida, el mismo cielo de donde un día, ruego Dios lo más lejos posible, te voy a mirar protegiéndote con todo mi amor.
De este cielo llegaste tu, Estrella luminosa que iluminaste mi camino, Angel bendecido que me mostraste otra cara de la vida.
Así, mirando el cielo, quiero  quedarme contigo, el mismo cielo al cual cada sueño se dirige.
El mío hoy es de hacer de toda tu vida un sueño porque tu ya cumpliste el mío llegando en mis brazos y llenando mi alma de amor cada segundo.
Al cielo pido que me deje mirar tus ojos cuándo reirán, secarlos cuando una lágrima los mojarán, al cielo pido que te proteja y que llene tu vida con los arcoíris más brillantes.
Gracias amor mío por ser el cielo que siempre soñé, gracias Dios por permitirme de vivir este sueño. 
Te amo Princesa mía y feliz dia del Padre para mí.

But Love is passion. Obsession. Someone you can’t live without. I say, fall head over heels, find someone you can love like crazy and who will love you the same way back. How can you find him? Well, you Forget your head, and you listen to your heart. And I’m not hearing any heart, because the truth is, honey, there’s no sense living your life without this. To make the journey and not fall deeply in love...well you haven’t lived a life at all. But you have to try because if you haven’t tried, you haven’t lived. 

Pero el amor es pasión.  Obsesión.  Alguien sin quien no puedes vivir.  Yo digo, enamorate perdidamente, encuentra a alguien a quien puedas amar como loco y que te amará de la misma manera.  Cómo lo encontraras? 
Bueno, olvida tu cabeza y escucha tu corazón.  Y yo no escucho ningún corazón, porque la verdad es, cariño, no tiene sentido vivir tu vida sin esto.  Hacer el viaje y no enamorarse profundamente significa que no has vivido una vida en absoluto.  Pero tienes que intentarlo porque si no lo has intentado, no has vivido 
@sharfonseca ❤️

Earlier this week, we had our daughter’s cleft palate surgery. It has been a very challenging and emotional week for us, and you can already imagine for her... having your little baby go through something so serious as a surgery, really shakes your whole world as a parent. Our angel really doesn’t ceases to amaze us! She was so brave, calm and sweet through it all, it makes me so proud to be her father! 
With tears in my eyes, I tell you that my heart goes out to all the parents that go through health experiences with their babies! Hope you guys are always protected. We are now home. We are so grateful and blessed! 🙏🏽❤️ 

A principios de esta semana, tuvimos la cirugía del paladar hendido de nuestra hija. Ha sido una semana muy desafiante y emotiva para nosotros, y ya se pueden imaginar para ella... que tu pequeño bebé pase por algo tan serio como una cirugía, realmente sacude todo tu mundo como padre. ¡Nuestro ángel realmente nunca nos deja de sorprendernos! Ella fue tan valiente, gentil y dulce a pesar de todo, ¡me enorgullece ser su padre! Con lágrimas en los ojos, les digo que mi corazón está con todos los padres que pasan por experiencias de salud con sus bebés. Espero que estén siempre protegidos. Ahora estamos en casa. ¡Estamos muy agradecidos y bendecidos! 🙏🏽❤️

Lunedi , il nostro piccolo angelo Blu,è stata operata per correggere la palatoschisi congenita . Sono stati giorni molto difficili, vedere una creatura innocente soffrire è un esperienza molto provante. Lei, con la sua dolcezza e la sua forza , ha attraversato questa tempesta con la calma e la forza di cui Dio l’ha dotata . Sono orgoglioso di essere suo padre e non laverò mai la maglia col suo sangue delle prime ore post operatorie nelle quali le mie braccia erano la sua unica certezza...voglio che rimanga ogni ricordo interno ed esterno di questa profonda lezione di coraggio che questo piccolo angelo ha dato a me e a Sharon.
Adesso siamo a casa e ringraziando Dio rivolgiamo un pensiero di solidarieta’ a tutti i genitori che stanno affrontando un problema di salute con le loro creature. 
Che Dio possa sempre proteggerli e benedirli. 🙏🏼❤️
@sharfonseca

With much love we want to share the story of the birth of our Blu Jerusalema. We are very happy that you finally get to meet her. 

Blu was born with a "cleft palate."
Immediately our soul and heart went with our daughter, but at the same time with the families who have gone through the same situation, since this happens to every 1 in 700 babies.

We are blessed to have a great medical team for our little girl, and that in due time, they will be able to proceed with surgery and thus help her live a completely normal life.

But this is not the situation for many families, and it is for this reason that we have decided to take this opportunity to spread awareness and support foundations like @operationsmile that are in charge of helping families in this situation.

 With love,

Sharon & Gianluca

————

Con mucho amor queremos compartir la historia del nacimiento de nuestra Blu Jerusalema. Estamos muy felices de que finalmente la conozcan.

Blu nació con “paladar hendido.” 
Inmediatamente nuestra alma y corazón se fueron con nuestra hija, pero al mismo tiempo con la cantidad de familias que han pasado por la misma situación, ya que esto sucede a cada 1 de 700 bebés. 

Tenemos la bendición de contar con un gran equipo médico para nuestra pequeña, y que a su debido tiempo, podran operarla y asi ayudarla a llevar una vida completamente normal. 

Pero esta no es la situación de muchas familias, y es por esta razón hemos decidido tomar esta oportunidad para difundir información y apoyar fundaciones como @operationsmile que se encargan de ayudar familias en esta situación. 

 Con amor, 

Sharon & Gianluca

Many times the female universe is wrongly defined as the weaker sex. I think that women are the backbone of society. 
 
Women have “balls” but they have them up in their head. 

For them, history has been very difficult. They have had to fight against prejudice. And many times against abuse.

I want to tell you something that is written in the Bible that always fascinated me: 
“Be very careful to make a woman cry, because God counts her tears. 
The woman came out of the rib of the man, not from the feet to be stepped on or from the head to be superior, but from the side, to be equal. A little bit below the arm to protect them and on the side of the heart to be loved.” 
#gvlifestyle

Today I want to talk about moralism. 

The world is full of moralists. They are the ones who live criticizing people who want to be themselves and find their pleasures. They always embrace the sense of guilt and norms. They say that living for ones desires is a guilt. But I think that when you do your duties, you also have the right to find your pleasures. So they “give up” on their pleasures, except their pleasure to criticize you! They think that people who smile, are not serious. On the contrary, I think that people who do not smile, are the ones that are not serious. They want you to be closed in a square of “norms” and they talk about ethics. However, they talk so much, they don’t have time to practice what they preach. Remember..their anger is envy with an “halo” .
#gvlifestyle

How many times in life you haven’t taken a decision because you were scared or fearful? This is normal! but you have to find the courage to face it. 
Plato said: “We can easily forgive a child who is afraid of the dark; the real tragedy of life is when men are afraid of the light.” 
Remember that not taking a decision is a decision. I wanna tell you a quote that has always inspired me: “One day the fear knocked on the door. The courage went to open and found no one.” Martin Luther King.
Fear exists, it is true, but you have the courage to beat it within yourself. 
Let me give you an advice: everyday try to do something that scares you and you’ll get used to face and conquer your fears! 
Enjoy
#gvlifestyle

Il nostro grande presidente Draghi ha gia' preso tutte le precauzioni preparando apposite linee affinche' le banche che pottebbero far fatica a finanziarsi sull'interbancario , abbiano possibilita di approvvigionamento di denaro comunque. Per quel che riguarda invece l'effetto "domino" potrebbe eventualmemte riguardare solo qualche paese dell'Europa Del Nord perche' nessun altro potrebbe pensare di uscire. In fin dei conti, in un trend sostanziaemte laterale, ogni tanto qualcuno deve alimentare motivi speculativi che come in questo caso saranno destinati ad esaurirsi con il risultato di aver creato qualche profitto da suggestione e il successivo rialzo quando la minaccia paventata scemera' come io penso. Questa è stata la fine del convegno di ieri...Lui è Sam, Sam Berns, affetto da progeria, una malattia rarissima che oggi colpisce 350 bambini nel mondo. In questo video Sam , all'epoca diciassettenne,racconta di quando gli fecero la domanda riguardo quale fosse la cosa più importante che la gente avrebbe dovuto sapere di lui . La sua risposta fu :" che ho una vita veramente felice" . Sam e' scomparso tre mesi dopo questo discorso. Di fronte a lui, che incarnava la gioia di vivere , mi inchino e invito tutti voi a fare altrettanto , pensando che se lui ha risposto così, è un dovere di tutti noi provare ad avere una vita felice. 
Grazie dell'esempio Sam🙏
